message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously crafted to provide exceptional value and quality. This product is worth more than $100 to me, but I believe in making it accessible to those who appreciate its unique benefits. I am offering it to you for $125. I understand that this might be a bit higher than what you might have expected, but I assure you, it comes with a guarantee of satisfaction and superior performance. If you're interested, please let me know, and we can proceed with the transaction.
